How to use

spawn 2 screens, 1 for the main screen second one for console screen if you want to use it (highly recommended)

spawn one button for each screen, this will be used to turn them on

spawn a wire text entry, this will become our keyboard

spawn the E2s

wire all the entities from the case e2

wire Power from these (Chat Reciever, Graphics Interface, Central Processing Unit, Sound Card and Case) to the Power Supply's Power

wire PowerCut from Case, Power Supply and Graphics Interface to a toggle button, you can place it behind the case

wire CPUUsage from Power Supply to Central Processing Unit's Usage

wire GPUUsage from Power Supply to Graphics Interface's Usage

wire CRUsage from Power Supply to Chat Reciever's Usage

wire LastSaid and LastSaidPerson from Central Processing Unit to Chat Reciever

wire String from Graphics Interface to Central Processing Unit's StringOut

wire ConsoleString from Graphics Interface to Central Processing Unit's ConsoleOut

wire Stop from Graphics Interface to Central Processing Unit's Stop

wire ScreenPower and ConsolePower from Graphics Interface to the Screens' power buttons

additionally you can spawn 1-4 props that work as speakers, each wired to the Sound Card

wire SoundName from Sound Card to Central Processing Unit


it's a lot of wiring but it's nice to keep everything separate

to start the computer, well just start a computer as you would normally do, don't forget to turn on the main power from the back

for commands it has only few atm i plan on making hard drives etc

commands:

play (song1-3)

start (chat, console) (dungeon master is not coded in yet)
